```
    SAFEHANDLEREF   m_safeHandle;
    LPVOID          m_handle;
    CLR_BOOL        m_hasThreadAffinity;
```

The [manged code](https://github.com/dotnet/coreclr/blob/9d932bb6af40e78c83d98ed280465c7024884d52/src/System.Private.CoreLib/src/System/Threading/WaitHandle.cs#L29-L35) uses this layout:

```c#
        private IntPtr waitHandle;
        internal volatile SafeWaitHandle _waitHandle;
        internal bool hasThreadAffinity;
```

Notice that the first two fields are reversed.

